title: Swansea City winger Nathan Dyer has been ruled out for the rest of the season after rupturing his achilles tendon in 2-0 win over Leicester City
text:
EFL Dyer blow Swansea City winger Nathan Dyer has been ruled out for the rest of the season after rupturing his achilles tendon in 2-0 win over Leicester City 
The Swans wide-man had to come off after just seven minutes in the tie at the Liberty Stadium against his former side by jake lambourne
